data.description: This charming home offers 3 generously sized bedrooms along with a separate den/office. With a 7,244 square foot lot, you'll have plenty of outdoor space and NO HOA! The home boasts of spacious kitchen and the bedrooms are equally impressive, offering an airy atmosphere. Nestled in a serene and quiet neighborhood, you'll find the peace and tranquility you've been searching for. This property is not just a house; it's a canvas for you to create your ideal lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make this home your own. Discover the endless possibilities that await in this quiet, spacious, and HOA-free gem!
